App Builder

App Builder is the first and unique visual development environment that allow you to create, with or without programming knowledge, HTML5 apps, WebApps, Progressive WebApps, WebExtensions and Hybrid apps for both mobile and desktop platforms.

HTML Compiler

HTML Compiler allows you to convert your HTML applications (e-books, presentations, games, put your imagination here!) in executable programs ready to use without any dependency.

NeoPlugins

Here you can found the larger VisualNeo plugins collection in the world. Get their advantage for your VisualNeo publications with a total of 59 plugins, 1139 actions, 235 examples.

Photo Compiler

Photo Compiler allows to create attractives, practices and useful galleries with your photos and images and then convert it into executable programs ready to be viewed without any dependency.

Screen GIF

Screen GIF allow us to grab and save certain choosed screen area directly and easily like an animated GIF image file ready to be used or shared what you wanted.

Img Converter

This program can convert images from up to 23 input formats to up to 18 output formats. To convert them, just drag and drop one or more image files into the program's main window.

Small Editor

Small Editor can be used to edit plain text and source code (recognize and highlight dozens of programming languages) lightweight, fast and effective. This website, for example, is edited using Small Editor.

Volume Keys

Change your speakers volume using whatever keyboard hotkey combinations of your choice. Be informed about the current volume level by the program's visual feedback.

Humm PHP

Humm PHP is an open source, lightweight, easy to use and free of charge website manager writen in the PHP language. The DecSoft's website, for example, is powered by Humm PHP.
